Kid‑Simple Version
ProjectCompass is a square with four sides:
Life
Mind
Truth
Love
In the middle is Center (the calm spot).
When the middle lifts up, the square becomes a pyramid. The top point is Apex.
Apex is the “up” feeling — like growing, learning, or feeling clear.
Flow is the line going up. Flow never stops. We just notice it sometimes.
Adult‑Clean Version
ProjectCompass organizes awareness through four quadrants — Life, Mind, Truth, and Love — with a central integration point. When the center is lifted, the structure becomes a pyramid, culminating in Apex, the crown state of coherence.
Flow is the upward axis from Center to Apex. Flow is continuous; only our participation in awareness of it changes. The Compass functions on both the Earthly Plane (ordinary awareness) and the Cosmic Plane (expanded awareness), providing a geometric model for balance, clarity, and ascent.
